                        <interp inst="t18460817-name-1016" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN COLE</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) The prisoner was given into my custody—he said he was not aware How the copper came there—I found this copper in his pocket.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I had not my jacket, waistcoat, or hat on all day—I had not been in the shop since seven o'clock in the morning, and never thought of looking into my hat.</p>
